block_<dir>	block someone unless they're invis or sneaking
block_all_<dir>	block someone no matter what
falling_room	makes a person fall down to the next room if they cant fly
		should check for feather fall (if so, just make em drift down)
ghost		makes a mob disappear but leave any stuff it had behind
		a way to make mobs not leave a corpse -- with modifications
		it could leave a corpse object kind of thing
